<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_230_r1l2"><expan>Lıebn</expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns aber <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>Chunrat<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvolfs ewrs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r1l3"><expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / dem Phılıpp Bewrlein vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ſelig ſchuldig <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r1l5">ſein ſol 
